What you need to know:

Meanwhile, sports betting firm Betika has extended support to some of Kenya’s professional golfers as well amateurs, who featured in last week’s Magical Kenya Open as well as this week’s Kenya Savannah Classic.Through the Betika na Community Initiative, the firm extended support worth Sh545,000 towards John Wangai of Sigona Club, Justus Madoya of the Great Rift Valley Club, Edwin Inana, Mathew Omondi and Isaac Makhoha all from the Vet Lab.